n him to spawn point (loc on graffe's), it is under one of the big bells in fear, very close to the middle of south wall. just turn 90 degree right from zone in and u wont miss it (abt 1000 loc points travel staright from there), or move to west wall (left) turn south (left) and keep runnig around the zone border (keeping it on ur right) there will be a deep flat cut into the south wall, the bell is more or les straight out north from there (u can see it if u know how it looks like), FD the monk at spawn point and /q outta there. next time just go in and FD staright away(the only mob that comes near is a wraith, its path crosses right under the bell).<br><br>oh and have one or the other insta gate potion on the monk just in case. (i have bouaght the 1200pp swirling mist potion for the purpose)<br><br>hope it help and i wud really appreciate if sum1 cud help me with some better ideas.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ueovandall.showPublicProfile?language=EN>eovandall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/21/02 9:27:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1840.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Fear golem Story</span><hr size=1> Where do you get this swirling mist potion, and where does it take you?<br>Eoooooooo <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyaldin111.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yaldin111</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/21/02 10:18:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1840.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   